布勞恩的父親喬（Joe）出生於[[以色列|以色列]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jewishchronicle.org/current/20070615/localnews.htm|title=Moving to the Big Leagues, Braun becomes next Jewish baseball hope|last=Nelles|first=Mitch|date=June 15, 2007|work=威斯康辛猶太記事報|accessdate=September 13, 2007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928035626/http://www.jewishchronicle.org/current/20070615/localnews.htm|archivedate=2007-09-28}}</ref>，在7歲時移民到美國<ref name="JStandard">{{cite news|url=http://www.jstandard.com/index.php/content/item/Rookie_could_make_history_151_but_will_he_cut_Yom_Kippur/|title=Rookie could make history - but will he cut Yom Kippur?|last=Abramowitz|first=Martin|date=August 31, 2007|work=猶太標準報|accessdate=September 13, 2007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120420011333/http://www.jstandard.com/index.php/content/item/Rookie_could_make_history_151_but_will_he_cut_Yom_Kippur|archivedate=2012-04-20}}</ref>。布勞恩是猶太人<ref name="JStandard"/>，他說：“這就是我感到自豪的地方。”<ref name="Hunt">{{cite news|url=http://www.jsonline.com/story/index.aspx?id=623892|title=Precocious Braun is in good company|last=Hunt|first=Michael|date=June 23, 2007|work=''密爾瓦基哨兵日報''|accessdate=September 13, 2007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929111409/http://www.jsonline.com/story/index.aspx?id=623892|archivedate=2007-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Boroson, Warren | url = http://www.jstandard.com/articles/4607/1/Why-Jews-love-baseball | title = Why Jews love baseball |publisher= ''猶太標準報'' | date = August 8, 2008 | accessdate = September 15, 2008}}</ref> 他的昵稱“希伯萊鐵錘”<ref name="Hunt"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2007/writers/gennaro_filice/08/24/fiveup.fivedown/|title=Five Up, Five Down|last=Filice|first=Gennaro|date=August 24, 2007|work=[[體育畫報|體育畫報]]|accessdate=September 13, 2007}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/page2/story?page=keri/070813&sportCat=mlb|title=Ten great baseball flicks that relate to this year's pennant races|last=Keri|first=Jonah|date=August 16, 2007|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|accessdate=September 13, 2007}}</ref> 指的就是猶太后裔，前釀酒人隊的[[漢克·阿倫|漢克·阿倫]]（他的外號是鐵錘漢克）以及電影''希伯萊鐵錘''。這也是他前隊友[[蓋比·凱普勒|蓋比·凱普勒]]（Gabe Kapler）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/spring2008/columns/story?columnist=crasnick_jerry&id=3260725|title=New faces, position changes for Brewers this spring|last=Crasnick|first=Jerry|date=February 24, 2008|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|accessdate=February 25, 2008}}</ref>，前全明星球員[[艾爾·羅森|艾爾·羅森]]（Al Rosen）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bioproj.sabr.org/bioproj.cfm?a=v&v=l&bid=1275&pid=12230|title=Al Rosen|last=Berger|first=Ralph|work=SABR|accessdate=September 13, 2007|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608074207/http://bioproj.sabr.org/bioproj.cfm?a=v&v=l&pid=12230&bid=1275|archive-date=2011-06-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 和[[漢克·格林伯格|漢克·格林伯格]]（Hank Greenberg）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailycal.org/printable.php?id=21367|title=Off Base...with Ryan Gorcey|last=Gorcey|first=Ryan|date=September 13, 2006|work=加州人日報|accessdate=September 13, 2007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927202656/http://www.dailycal.org/printable.php?id=21367|archivedate=2007-09-27}}</ref> 的昵稱。

