 2009 | accessdate = October 1, 2009 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091003090013/http://www.dailynews.com/sports/ci_13458822 | archivedate =2009-10-03}}</ref>。“並沒有太多的猶太裔運動員能達到這種高度，”布勞恩說，“很榮幸我是其中之一。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article_perspectives.jsp?ymd=20080714&content_id=3135051&vkey=perspectives&fext=.jsp|title="Braun shows brain to handle spotlight; Brewers star deftly manages mental, athletic aspects of game"|last=Burman|first=Mike|date=July 15, 2008|work= ''MLB.com'' |accessdate=March 1, 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.jewishjournal.com/cover_story/article/jordan_farmar_and_the_jewish_hoops_future_20090422/ | author = Greenberg, Brad A | title = Jordan Farmar and the Jewish (Hoops) Future; The NBA's lone MOT is down but not out of Laker's postseason, | work = ''猶太日報'' | date = 2009-04-22 | accessdate = 4/23/2009-04-23}}</ref>

===高中時期===
布勞恩高中四年都是格拉納達山高中棒球隊的頭號球星，其中三年擔任隊長，並且獲得MVP。他高中時期守游擊的位置，三年級前還曾擔任過投手。2000年，高二的布勞恩打擊率高達4成56。高四那年上壘率達到了6成75，並以25支全壘打打破了校史的紀錄<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.madison.com/wsj/home/sports/brewers/202345 | author = Mulhern, Tom | title = Brewers: Braun's start a smashing success | work = ''威斯康星州日報'' | date = 2007-07-21 | accessdate = 2007-12-20 | archive-date = 2008-04-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080421054753/http://www.madison.com/wsj/home/sports/brewers/202345 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。他也在''Team One Baseball''評選的全國最佳游擊手新秀中名列第六<ref>{{cite web | url = http://media.www.thehurricaneonline.com/media/storage/paper479/news/2004/02/06/Sports/Braun.Hopes.To.Live.Up.To.Lofty.Expectations-599571.shtml | author = Kalis, Eric | title = Braun hopes to live up to lofty expectations | work = ''The Hurricane'' | date = 2004-02-06 | accessdate = 2007-06-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927031402/http://media.www.thehurricaneonline.com/media/storage/paper479/news/2004/02/06/Sports/Braun.Hopes.To.Live.Up.To.Lofty.Expectations-599571.shtml | archivedate = 2007-09-27 }}</ref>，並且被[[美國棒球|美國棒球]]雜志選入百大最佳新秀之中。2002年布勞恩並沒有大聯盟球隊選擇他，因為他說他將要進入大學學習<ref name=MiamiProfile>{{cite web | url = http://hurricanesports.cstv.com/sports/m-basebl/mtt/braun_ryan00.html | title = Ryan Braun profile | work = Miami Hurricanes | accessdate = 2007-02-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070311133148/http://hurricanesports.cstv.com/sports/m-basebl/mtt/braun_ryan00.html | archivedate = 2007-03-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/news;_ylt=AtieJCL2Bbuyr_2ZayN.Vk8RvLYF?slug=gettoknowbrewersbryanbra&prov=tsn&type=lgns | author = Crossman, Matt | title = Get to know Brewers 3B Ryan Braun | work = ''體育新聞'' | date = 2007-08-08 | accessdate = 2007-09-10}}</ref>。

===大學時期===
盡管[[斯坦福大學|斯坦福大學]]和[[伯克利加州大學|伯克利加州大學]]提供獎學金，但布勞恩還是選擇[[邁阿密大學_(佛羅里達州)|邁阿密大學]]。他選擇邁阿密大學的原因包括了學校在學術、運動、社會等方面的成就。布勞恩在大一擊出了17支全壘打和76分打點，打擊率高達3成64。他獲得了全國年度最佳新人的榮譽，並入選全美新人第一隊<ref name=MiamiProfile/>。

大三這年是布勞恩在大學期間最成功的一年，這個賽季開始他從游擊手轉為三壘手，打擊率達到3成96，長打率更是高達7成26，並有18支全壘打、76分打點和23次盜壘成功。他的長打率和打點在[[全國大學體育協會|NCAA]]第一級分別排在第9和第10位，並被[[美國棒球|美國棒球]]雜志選為全美大學最佳陣容。他還獲得了當年的金槍獎提名<ref name=MiamiProfile/>，[[大西洋沿岸聯盟|大西洋沿岸聯盟]]年度最佳棒球運動員的榮譽<ref name=Boo>{{cite book | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=aFkwyOIHsr8C&pg=PA317&lpg=PA317&dq=Aleksandra+Wozniak+jewish&source=bl&ots=ALnKiS6X2u&sig=6nAYWJHYDNa4j5xOAd5Rq47jDcM&hl=en&ei=QOwiSsvdDpzFtge04_XcBg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3#v=onepage&q=&f=false | author = Wechsler, Robert | title = ''Day by Day in Jewish Sports History'' | pages = 144 | publisher = Ktav Publishing House | year = 2007 | isbn = 0881259691 | accessdate = 2009-10-13}}</ref>。

== 職業生涯 ==
=== 密爾瓦基釀酒人 ===
{{MLBy|2007年}}布勞恩首次進入大聯盟春訓營<ref name=GBP>{{cite web | url = http://www.greenbaypressgazette.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20070125/GPG0206/70125182/1225/GPGsports | title = Brewers GM: 'We feel we are a much better ballclub this year' | work = ''綠灣新聞報'' | date = 2007-01-25 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。球隊之前的三壘手[[科里·克斯基|科里·克斯基]]（Corey Koskie）得了腦震蕩後綜合徵，錯過了春訓，最終也錯過了整個賽季<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rotowire.com/roto_to_gnews.htm?ID=208088&sport=mlb | title = Corey Koskie: Not Ready for Spring Training | author = Rotowire | accessdate = 2007-02-20}}</ref>。球隊計劃使用[[克雷格·康塞爾|克雷格·康塞爾]]和[[托尼·格拉菲尼諾|托尼·格拉菲尼諾]]（Tony Graffanino）作為球隊的開季陣容，同時也多觀察布勞恩。在春訓的第一場比賽，布勞恩表現十分出色，5個打數擊出4支安打，包括了一支[[滿貫全壘打|滿貫全壘打]]，一支三分全壘打，一支二壘安打，一支一壘安打以及一次盜壘成功，並有7分打點入賬<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/news/boxscore.jsp?gid=2007_03_02_milmlb_sfnmlb_1 | title = Boxscore | work = ''MLB.com'' | date = 2007-03-02 | accessdate = 2007-09-11}}</ref>。在總共11場比賽當中，他的打擊率高達3成53，長打率更是達到驚人的.912，15分的打點排名大聯盟第二，盡管他還錯過了7場比賽<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/stats/league_leaders.jsp?c_id=mlb&baseballScope=NL&statType=1&sortByStat=HR&timeSubFrame3=&timeSubFrame=23&Submit=Submit&timeFrame=1 | title = League Leaders | work = ''MLB.com'' | accessdate = 2007-09-11}}</ref>。但同時他也有4次的守備失誤。3月20日布勞恩被送回小聯盟春訓營，釀酒人隊總教練[[內德·約斯特|內德·約斯特]]（Ned Yost）評論布勞恩時說道：“他在打擊方面做得非常出色，但守備還需要提高。他明白他需要做什麼。他確實非常接近（大聯盟）。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.beloitdailynews.com/articles/2007/03/20/sports/sports11.txt | title = Brewers reassign Braun to Triple A | work = ''畢洛伊特每日新聞報'' | date = 2007-03-20 | accessdate = 2007-09-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181216031315/https://www.beloitdailynews.com/articles/2007/03/20/sports/sports11.txt | archive-date = 2018-12-16 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>
2013年，布勞恩效力的61場比賽中，繳出了14支二壘安打、9支全壘打、38分打點以及打擊率0.298的成績。2013年7月23日，布勞恩因為違反大聯盟禁藥政策，已被勒令禁賽至本球季結束。<ref>{{cite web|title=Doping Tarnishes Baseball Again as Brewers’ Braun Is Suspended|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/23/sports/baseball/ryan-braun-suspended-for-doping.html?emc=edit_na_20130722&_r=0|publisher=NY Times|accessdate=23 July 2013}}</ref>

2021年9月14日，布勞恩宣布從球員生涯退休<ref>{{cite news |title=Milwaukee Brewers slugger Ryan Braun announces retirement |url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/32208038/milwaukee-brewers-slugger-ryan-braun-announces-retirement |access-date=2021-09-15 |publisher=ESPN.com |date=2021-09-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=McCalvy |first1=Adam |title=Ryan Braun retires after 14 seasons |url=https://www.mlb.com/brewers/news/ryan-braun-announces-retirement |access-date=2021-09-15 |publisher=MLB.com |date=2021-09-14}}</ref>。

